b'WELCOME TO THE UNIVERSITY OF ILLINOIS AT CHICAGO'
b'\xe2\x80\x9cPrograms for International Partnerships will be an active and essential contributor to the global engagement efforts at UIC, offering unique and innovative partnership programs to meet the needs of stakeholders both on campus and around the world.\xe2\x80\x9d'
b'Since its inception in 1992, the Programs for International Partnerships (PIP)\xc2\xa0 has welcomed more than 10,000 Asian professionals to the U.S. Utilizing strong academics of the University of Illinois and its close ties with all levels of governments and professional organizations, PIP can customize degree and non-degree programs to meet the specific needs of groups of government officials, business and corporate managers, educators, academic researchers, and students.'
b'We invite you to take advantage of the opportunity to meet your professional, academic and personal needs through studying with world-renowned faculty, on an attractive campus within one of the most dynamic cities in the world, Chicago!'
